1. identation is always necessary in if-else statement.
2. always use colon (:) 
3. can have multiple print statement
4. we can use boolean variables directly for conditioning
eg- 
if 30>20:
    print("yes")
    print("it is correct)
eg- 
login_in= "True"
if login_in:
    print("correct")

